{
  "stem": "3022.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And before they were being put on the, on the, on the trains, on the cattle cars, this beautiful girl having come to him, to the, the drug store, and asking for quinine because she wanted to abort.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And as he was a describing her, I said, wait a minute.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I went to my uncle's locker and I took out a picture of my cousin, and I brought it to him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he says, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That was her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She was pregnant.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I never told my uncle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I never told her husband, who was in the camp with me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were taken to Belzec, and as we later learned, at the time that they, they were given to live from the time they were-- that they came off the train to the gas chambers, about four hours.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So later on, I-- we surmised that they died on Thisa B'Av.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I verified it when I went to Washington to the Holocaust Museum, and I checked out the dates.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My, my father's family perished on Thisa B'Av, which is a day of mourning-- [COUGHS] For Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The camp to which we came already had several hundred people in it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Most of them came from the town of Mielec, and the town of Radomysl.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "These were Jewish people who really didn't have any professions before that, but they all declared themselves that they were either machinist, or, or, or, or carpenters, or electricians in order to, to, to get a job that, that might save their lives.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "What-- this was-- before the war, it was the center of Polish defense industry.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And now they were manufacturing parts for the Heinkel 111, also repairing other German planes that were being damaged during the German-Russian war.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
